The Devil Woman hitmaker rocked up at the star-studded sports event in one of his signature garish suits. Addressing his outlandish outfit, pundits exclaimed: "You will not see another suit like that!" Cliff donned a blue and yellow snakeskin print jacket and matching shirt, which he paired with a blue zig-zag print tie. The star wore his signature sunglasses as he arrived at the sporting event with a large smile on his face. Cliff finished his outfit with a pair of navy trousers and a red rose pinned to his lapel.